Green campus initiative

August 2023 the University begins a green campus, in the school, the initiate deals with planting of tree and environmental climate change.[8]
Convocation

On 9 December the University hold is 13th convocation ceremony in which 1584 students are graduated from the school.[9]
Scholarship

On the 13th convocation ceremony of the school the speaker of the event announces sponsorship for female indigent students at the school. 

